{"title":"城市风景（新古诗）","authors":["刘征"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（新古诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土气挂西装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡音混京腔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焉知不化龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鱼闯大江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王总好书法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李总好丹青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘总好写诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗集获好评。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻环卫工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不好多说话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个小书房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存书一架架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越变越好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一看一回新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白头老住户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻作旅游人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襟沾五洲雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩披远洋风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二老旅游归，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿开车迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的哥坐车上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商女立摊头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老外来相问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英语答如流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时装袒肩背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长发染金黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头赏新美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无人道短长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥甘已吃厌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想食家乡饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着避喧嚣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住进农家院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年不见燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久不问鸡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶然闻犬吠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女郎身后追。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫步步行街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步见丛花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小坐街头椅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝杯龙井茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芒果东南亚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脐橙美利坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杂陈五洲果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小水果摊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标题眼迷乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图像亮而鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活万花筒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头小报摊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这家炸酱面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那家肯德基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饮食求适口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必分东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新楼如春笋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时才露芽尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几日不曾见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌出万重山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边荒废地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来变花坛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花坛又一变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成小公园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三代居老屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋瓦生青草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆迁住高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芳草楼边绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼前一片绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳台几盆花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门泊新轿车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻常百姓家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}